    {
      "id": "PopularPost224670",
      "post_content": "Yes, [Arrest](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Arrest) is more powerful, but also three times as expensive to cast ( understandably, this might suck down more mana through the course of a game, but that's another matter. ) And [Pacifism](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pacifism) won't and can't shut down activated abilities. And since you can drop it T1( though likely T2 in response to their T1, ) that means you can shut down a lot of mana acceleration creatures early in the game where their impact is greater.  \n  \nMight not see much use in highly competitive tourneys, but in the realms of kitchen table and limited where you're likely mana-rich, it's certainly an attractive option. This card saved a lot of games for me at the pre-release event.",
      "posted_by": "RedJaron",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost224670\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">Yes, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Arrest\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Arrest\">Arrest</a> is more powerful, but also three times as expensive to cast ( understandably, this might suck down more mana through the course of a game, but that's another matter. )  And <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Pacifism\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pacifism\">Pacifism</a> won't and can't shut down activated abilities.  And since you can drop it T1( though likely T2 in response to their T1, ) that means you can shut down a lot of mana acceleration creatures early in the game where their impact is greater.<br/><br/>Might not see much use in highly competitive tourneys, but in the realms of kitchen table and limited where you're likely mana-rich, it's certainly an attractive option.  This card saved a lot of games for me at the pre-release event.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '224670'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy76650\">RedJaron</span>\r\n                                (1/29/2012 4:15:11 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n